<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Dear <%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %>,</p>
    
    <p>You are now successfully registered on <%= appName %>. Please login and begin using <%= appName %>.</p>

    <p>Best Wishes,<br>
    <%= appName %></p>

    <hr>

    <p>You received this email because you are registered on <%= appName %> with the email address: <%= user.email %></p>
</body>
</html>
